data.description: First Time available hand crafted, Rustic,  1 1/2 story - 3 bed 2 bath , about 1380 Sq. Ft. built in 2019, nestled in the tall ponderosa pines at North Fork.  Wood stove with a rock fireplace, Wooden beams and rocks all used from the property.Custom counters, counter tops, barn doors, pine floors.  Built in drawers in the bedroom along with a king size bed with drawers that will remain.  Rustic and comfortable on 35+ acres, secluded nicely.  Shop, greenhouse, chicken coops and a meditation cabin, or whatever you want to use it for.  Also a campsite below the house for your company, Come see this listing today, you won't be disappointed!  Drone footage is on its way!  ALSO, POA offers a greenbelt open to the residents of North Fork Ranches with fishing and a new pavilion for your get togethers.
